<section id="rotate" class="section">
    <div class="py-4 px-2 px-sm-4">
        <div class="section-heading mb-4">
            <a class="d-flex justify-content-between section-toggle text-decoration-none"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#rotCollapse" role="button" 
                aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="rotCollapse">
                <h2 class="display-6 w-100 d-flex m-0">
                    Caesar cipher
                </h2>
                <span class="text-light px-1 border rounded align-self-end toggle-button">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up lh-base"></i>
                </span>
            </a>
            <hr>
            <p class="px-2">
                A very simple method of encription, the Caesar cipher - also known as a shift cipher - 'shifts' the alphabet a certain number of spaces, pushing the letters at the end to the beginning.
                The most common Caeser cipher is Rot 13, where 
                <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">A</code> 
                becomes 
                <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">N</code> 
                and so forth. You can optionally add a key to the cipher to further encrypt your results, this will create a custom alphabet to rotate through &ndash;
                 see the <a href="#sub" class="text-convrtr">Substiution Cipher</a> below for more information.
            </p>
            <p class="px-2">
                 There is more information available on the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caesar_cipher" class="text-convrtr">Caesar_cipher</a> Wikipedia page. 
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse show" id="rotCollapse">
            <ul class="pagination justify-content-center flex-wrap" id="pagination">
                {% for char in alpha %}
                    {% if forloop.first %}
                    <li class="page-item">
                        <button type="button" class="page-link" id="rotPrev" aria-label="Previous" 
                                data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Previous">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                        </button>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                    <li class="page-item">
                        <button type="button" class="page-link rot-link" id="rot{{ forloop.index }}" 
                            aria-label="Letter {{ char.letter | downcase }} - Rot {{ forloop.index }}" data-rot-number="{{ forloop.index }}" 
                            data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Rot {{ forloop.index }}">
                            <span class="visually-hidden">Letter</span> {{ char.letter | downcase }}<span class="visually-hidden"> - Rot {{ forloop.index }}</span>
                        </button>
                    </li>
                    {% if forloop.last %}
                    <li class="page-item">
                        <button type="button" class="page-link" id="rotNext" aria-label="Next" 
                                data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Next">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                        </button>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <span class="card-label visually-hidden">ROT Cipher</span>
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <textarea placeholder="Example: TEST â†’ YJXY (Rot 5)" title="ROT Text - text to substitute" rows="6" id="rotText" class="form-control rot-text" autocomplete="off"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer py-3">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4 g-0">
                            <div class="row row-cols-2 g-md-0 gx-0 gy-2">
                                <div class="col col-12 col-md-auto">
                                    <div class="input-group w-auto">
                                        <label class="input-group-text" id="rot-group" for="rotKey"><span class="visually-hidden">Caesar Cipher </span>Key</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="rotKey" autocomplete="off">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-md-auto flex-fill">
                                    <div class="row row-cols-auto g-0">
                                        <div class="col col-8 col-sm-auto ms-0 mx-md-2 me-auto">
                                            <div class="form-check form-switch text-start">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="chainRots" aria-checked="false">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="chainRots">Chain <span class="visually-hidden">rotation </span>commands</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col d-flex flex-fill justify-content-end">
                                            {% include "components/select-copy-dl" %}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                        <div id="rotResults" class="data-to-copy active"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>